[ GASPING ]

236
00:11:07,801 --> 00:11:09,235
OH, CRAP!

237
00:11:09,235 --> 00:11:11,572
SHE WENT AND TURNED
ALL THE KIDS INTO ZOMBIES.

238
00:11:11,572 --> 00:11:13,406
THIS IS MIND STITCHING.

239
00:11:13,406 --> 00:11:17,544
I’VE SEWN MY BASTING THREAD
RIGHT INTO THEIR BRAINS.

240
00:11:17,544 --> 00:11:19,513
GET HER, MY PUPPETS.

241
00:11:19,513 --> 00:11:20,947
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

242
00:11:23,449 --> 00:11:24,885
LADY SATSUKI!

243
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:29,022
[ TWINKLE! ]

244
00:11:31,224 --> 00:11:32,358
STAY SHARP.

245
00:11:32,358 --> 00:11:34,327
CONSIDER ALL WHO ATTACK
TO BE YOUR ENEMY.

246
00:11:34,327 --> 00:11:39,566
UNTIL WE DEFEAT RAGYO, YOU MUST
TURN YOUR HEARTS TO STEEL.

247
00:11:39,566 --> 00:11:41,735
LIFE FIBER OVERRIDE.

248
00:11:41,735 --> 00:11:44,404
KAMUI JUNKETSU!

249
00:11:46,106 --> 00:11:47,674
[ GRUNTS ]

250
00:11:47,674 --> 00:11:49,910
[ TROOPS SCREAMING ]

251
00:11:53,213 --> 00:11:55,315
OH! THAT SHOWOFF!

252
00:11:55,315 --> 00:11:56,850
[ GASPS ]

253
00:11:57,951 --> 00:11:59,920
[ TROOPS SCREAMING ]

254
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:02,388
RYUKO,
GO DEAL WITH RAGYO.

255
00:12:02,388 --> 00:12:03,890
WE CAN HANDLE THESE GUYS.

256
