258
00:12:07,093 --> 00:12:09,362
BELIEVING SATSUKI KIRYUIN
PLANNED THIS.

259
00:12:09,362 --> 00:12:10,597
I KNOW, RIGHT?

260
00:12:10,597 --> 00:12:14,034
BUT AT THIS POINT, I DON’T
CARE WHO BRINGS RAGYO DOWN.

261
00:12:14,034 --> 00:12:16,870
DAMN IT!
WHAT DID WE EVEN COME HERE FOR?

262
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:18,505
[ SCREAMS ]

263
00:12:22,943 --> 00:12:26,112
YOU WON’T ESCAPE ME,
RAGYO KIRYUIN.

264
00:12:26,112 --> 00:12:29,249
EVEN THOUGH YOU BETRAYED ME,
I’M IMPRESSED.

265
00:12:29,249 --> 00:12:33,453
BUT I’M AFRAID YOU’VE MADE
ONE GIGANTIC MISTAKE.

266
00:12:33,453 --> 00:12:34,688
HUH?

267
00:12:34,688 --> 00:12:35,889
[ GRUNTING ]

268
00:12:35,889 --> 00:12:37,591
[ SCREAMS ]

269
00:12:37,591 --> 00:12:38,959
MATOI!

270
00:12:38,959 --> 00:12:41,361
Senketsu:
I CAN’T UNDO THIS THREAD.

271
00:12:41,361 --> 00:12:44,130
[ GRUNTS ]

272
00:12:44,130 --> 00:12:46,600
BRINGING THE MATOI GIRL
INTO THE PICTURE

273
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,334
WAS A BAD MOVE
ON YOUR PART.

274
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,408
[ GRUNTS ]

275
00:12:55,408 --> 00:12:57,944
