SHE’D FIGHT FOR YOU.

276
00:12:57,944 --> 00:13:01,548
BUT AFTER A LITTLE
MIND STITCHING, SHE’S MY PAWN.

277
00:13:01,548 --> 00:13:02,983
[ GROWLS ]

278
00:13:02,983 --> 00:13:05,151
IT’S SUCH A TRAGIC TURN.

279
00:13:05,151 --> 00:13:08,088
[ GROWLS ]

280
00:13:08,088 --> 00:13:10,891
[ TWINKLE! TWINKLE! TWINKLE! ]

281
00:13:13,059 --> 00:13:15,896
THAT MUCH POWER
WITHOUT SYNCHRONIZING?

282
00:13:15,896 --> 00:13:17,430
MAGNIFICENT.

283
00:13:17,430 --> 00:13:21,802
IT APPEARS THE GIRL HAS
THE INNATE ABILITY TO SUMMON IT.

284
00:13:21,802 --> 00:13:25,005
[ STRAINING ]
CONTROL YOURSELF!

285
00:13:28,809 --> 00:13:29,976
I GOT YOU!

286
00:13:29,976 --> 00:13:32,879
SHINGAN‐TENSENZUKI!

287
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,081
CRAP!

288
00:13:35,081 --> 00:13:38,318
MON MIGNON PRêT‐à‐PORTER!

289
00:13:38,318 --> 00:13:39,452
[ TWINKLE! ]

290
00:13:39,452 --> 00:13:40,787
[ GRUNTS ]

291
00:13:40,787 --> 00:13:43,223
Nui: YOU’D BE MORE FUN IF YOU
GUYS WEREN’T SO UPTIGHT.

292
00:13:43,223 --> 00:13:45,959
I’M GONNA LET MY CUTE LITTLE
DOPPELGANGERS FIGHT YOU.

293
00:13:45,959 --> 00:13:48,261
MAYBE THEN YOU’LL REMEMBER
HOW TO HAVE FUN.

294
00:13:48,261 --> 00:13:50,897
TA‐TA!

295
00:13:50,897 --> 00:13:52,833
[ SCREAMS ]

296
00:14:02,042 --> 00:14:04,811
MATOI, SNAP OUT OF IT.

297
00:14:04,811 --> 00:14:06,880
I’M SORRY,
BUT YOUR LITTLE FRIEND

298
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:08,949
WILL NEVER BREAK FREE
OF MY CONTROL.

299
00:14:08,949 --> 00:14:13,219
I HAVE HER NERVOUS SYSTEM
TIED UP GOOD AND TIGHT.

300
00:14:14,721 --> 00:14:17,891
[ SNARLS, SCREAMS ]

301
00:14:17,891 --> 00:14:20,527
I SAID, "CONTROL YOURSELF"!

302
00:14:36,209 --> 00:14:41,214
DON’T...SCREW...WITH...ME!

303
00:14:42,883 --> 00:14:44,084
NO.

304
00:14:44,084 --> 00:14:47,253
WE AIN’T YOUR PUPPETS.

305
00:14:47,253 --> 00:14:55,328
I WON’T LET YOU TIE US DOWN
WITH SOME GODDAMN STRING!

306
00:14:56,830 --> 00:14:59,199
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

307
00:15:02,803 --> 00:15:04,204
BUT THAT’S IMPOSSIBLE.

308
00:15:04,204 --> 00:15:07,373
HOW COULD ANYONE BREAK FREE
OF YOUR MIND STITCHING?

309
00:15:07,373 --> 00:15:09,142
THIS FEELING...

310
00:15:09,142 --> 00:15:10,577
IT CAN’T BE.

311
00:15:10,577 --> 00:15:13,279
[ SCOFFS ] IT SEEMS
YOUR ANNOYING PERSONALITY

312
00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:14,681
HAS SAVED YOU YET AGAIN.

313
00:15:14,681 --> 00:15:17,684
I GOT SERIOUS BONES
TO PICK WITH YOU AFTER THIS,

314
00:15:17,684 --> 00:15:20,621
BUT TILL THEN,
WOULD YOU QUIT RAZZING ON ME?

315
00:15:21,722 --> 00:15:24,691
BITCH IS GOING DOWN ‐‐
HARD!

316
00:15:24,691 --> 00:15:27,160
LA VIE EST JUSTE DRôLE.

317
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:29,530
READY, SENKETSU?
SENKETSU: Ready!

318
00:15:29,530 --> 00:15:31,965
LIFE IS SO TRULY...

319
00:15:32,866 --> 00:15:34,300
...AMUSING.

320
00:15:37,871 --> 00:15:40,607
LONG TIME NO SEE, RYUKO.

321
00:15:40,607 --> 00:15:44,945
NUI...HARIME!

322
00:15:44,945 --> 00:15:46,379
YOU KNOW HOW SATSUKI
TOLD YOU

323
00:15:46,379 --> 00:15:48,782
THE WHOLE KILLING‐YOUR‐DADDY
THING WAS HER IDEA?

324
00:15:48,782 --> 00:15:49,983
IT WASN’T.

325
00:15:49,983 --> 00:15:51,685
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO!

326
00:15:51,685 --> 00:15:52,886
IT WAS A LIE.

327
00:15:52,886 --> 00:15:55,121
LADY RAGYO AND I
WERE BEHIND IT.

328
00:15:55,121 --> 00:15:57,558
YOU STILL WANT TO GET YOUR
HANDS ON THE SCISSOR BLADE?

329
00:15:57,558 --> 00:15:58,659
THEN COME ON.

330
00:15:58,659 --> 00:16:01,227
AVENGE YOUR DEAR OLD DEAD DADDY
RIGHT NOW.

331
00:16:01,227 --> 00:16:03,363
JUST DON’T BLAME ME
IF YOUR QUEST FOR REVENGE

332
00:16:03,363 --> 00:16:05,532
KILLS YOU, OKAY?
[ GROWLS ]

333
00:16:05,532 --> 00:16:07,467
[ GRUNTS ]

334
00:16:07,467 --> 00:16:10,303
Ryuko:
KIRYUIN, RAGYO’S ALL YOURS.

335
00:16:10,303 --> 00:16:14,608
SHE WAS NEVER ANYONE ELSE’S
TO BEGIN WITH.

336
00:16:14,608 --> 00:16:18,579
DEFEATING HER
HAS BEEN MY LIFE’S AMBITION.

337
00:16:18,579 --> 00:16:21,381
[ SIGHS ]

338
00:16:22,816 --> 00:16:25,051
♪ DON’T LOSE YOUR WAY ♪

339
00:16:25,051 --> 00:16:26,920
♪ IN YOUR MIND ♪

340
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:30,390
♪ WE HAVE TO BE AS ONE ♪

341
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:33,894
♪ DON’T BE AFRAID ♪

342
00:16:33,894 --> 00:16:35,328
♪ MY SWEETHEART ♪

343
00:16:35,328 --> 00:16:36,930
LIFE FIBERS...SYNCHRONIZE.

344
00:16:36,930 --> 00:16:38,965
KAMUI SENKETSU!

345
00:16:38,965 --> 00:16:42,936
♪ HARBOR MY DEEP SECRET ♪

346
00:16:42,936 --> 00:16:45,672
♪ IT MAKES ME SO BLUE ♪

347
00:16:45,672 --> 00:16:47,073
WHAT’S UP?

348
00:16:47,073 --> 00:16:49,209
I DON’T REMEMBER
YOU BEING THIS SLOW BEFORE.

349
00:16:49,209 --> 00:16:50,443
[ STRAINING ]

350
00:16:50,443 --> 00:16:53,413
MON MIGNON PRêT‐à‐PORTER!

351
00:16:53,413 --> 00:16:56,650
YOU THINK YOUR LITTLE SCRAPS
CAN STOP ME?

352
00:16:58,351 --> 00:16:59,520
NO WAY!

353
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,287
AW.
WHAT’S THE MATTER?

354
00:17:01,287 --> 00:17:03,023
YOU FEELING OKAY?

355
00:17:03,023 --> 00:17:04,891
YOU’RE LOOKING
KIND OF WORRIED.

356
00:17:04,891 --> 00:17:07,093
SENKETSU: Ryuko...
YOU’RE NOT GONNA
GIVE ME CRAP

357
00:17:07,093 --> 00:17:08,795
ABOUT GETTING FIRED UP AGAIN,
ARE YOU?

358
00:17:08,795 --> 00:17:10,664
No. The opposite.
HUH?

359
00:17:10,664 --> 00:17:13,967
We’ve never been
so in sync before.

360
00:17:13,967 --> 00:17:18,004
Right now, you and I
are behaving as one.

361
00:17:18,004 --> 00:17:21,274
This is Life Fiber
Synchronization!

362
00:17:21,274 --> 00:17:24,711
ALL RIGHT!
DAMN, THIS FEELS AWESOME, HUH?!

363
00:17:29,215 --> 00:17:32,853
HOW CAN AN ORDINARY HUMAN
HAVE THIS MUCH POWER?

364
00:17:32,853 --> 00:17:34,487
STAND ASIDE!

365
00:17:38,158 --> 00:17:41,628
RAGYO KIRYUIN, YOU’LL PAY
FOR TAKING THE LIFE

366
00:17:41,628 --> 00:17:44,497
OF MY FATHER,
SOICHIRO KIRYUIN...

367
00:17:44,497 --> 00:17:47,901
AND FOR THE LIFE
OF MY BABY SISTER!

368
00:17:47,901 --> 00:17:49,035
REALLY?

369
00:17:49,035 --> 00:17:51,037
ALL THIS
OVER SOME VENDETTA?

370
00:17:51,037 --> 00:17:53,273
HOW AWFULLY TRIVIAL
OF YOU.

371
00:17:53,273 --> 00:17:55,676
YOU GAVE YOUR HUMANITY
TO LIFE FIBERS,

372
00:17:55,676 --> 00:17:56,843
SO WHO ARE YOU TO JUDGE?

373
00:17:56,843 --> 00:18:00,046
ONLY A HUMAN
WOULD UNDERSTAND A NOBLE CAUSE.

374
00:18:00,046 --> 00:18:02,215
KILLING ME
WON’T BE SO EASY.

375
00:18:02,215 --> 00:18:05,786
I DOUBT EVEN A MONSTER LIKE YOU
COULD SURVIVE...

376
00:18:05,786 --> 00:18:07,187
WITHOUT A HEAD!

377
00:18:07,187 --> 00:18:08,288
[ GASPS ]

378
00:18:08,288 --> 00:18:11,157
AND NOW I’LL HAVE IT!

379
00:18:16,229 --> 00:18:18,131
LADY RAGYO!

380
00:18:25,138 --> 00:18:27,107
IT IS DONE.

381
00:18:36,216 --> 00:18:37,818
WHAT’S GOING ON?

382
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:41,888
[ SHOUTING ]

383
00:18:41,888 --> 00:18:45,125
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]
SHIRO!

384
00:18:47,628 --> 00:18:49,663
HONNOUJI ACADEMY!

385
00:18:49,663 --> 00:18:51,798
DOES ANYONE COPY?

386
00:18:51,798 --> 00:18:54,400
HONNOUJI ACADEMY!

387
00:18:58,171 --> 00:19:00,306
WHAT WAS THAT?

388
00:19:00,306 --> 00:19:03,644
IT IS <i>YOU</i>
<i>WHO ARE DONE, SATSUKI.</i>

389
00:19:03,644 --> 00:19:04,678
[ GASPS ]

390
00:19:09,015 --> 00:19:11,084
FINISH WHAT YOU START...

391
00:19:11,084 --> 00:19:12,753
FOR AS LONG
AS A STRAND OF THREAD

392
00:19:12,753 --> 00:19:18,224
CONNECTS MY HEAD TO MY BODY,
I CAN ALWAYS REGENERATE MYSELF.

393
00:19:18,224 --> 00:19:20,160
AND IT APPEARS YOUR BAKUZAN

394
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:23,129
CANNOT SEVER
ALL THE CONNECTING THREADS.

395
00:19:23,129 --> 00:19:24,898
IMPOSSIBLE.

396
00:19:24,898 --> 00:19:26,266
Together: LADY SATSUKI!

397
00:19:26,266 --> 00:19:28,835
STAY DOWN, YOU DOGS.

398
00:19:28,835 --> 00:19:30,070
[ GRUNTS, CHOKES ]

399
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:34,407
DEAR, WHAT WE HAVE HERE
IS A CASE OF MISUNDERSTANDING.

400
00:19:34,407 --> 00:19:36,677
THE FACT IS,
YOU ONLY <i>THINK</i>

401
00:19:36,677 --> 00:19:38,612
YOU’RE WEARING JUNKETSU
PROPERLY.

402
00:19:38,612 --> 00:19:40,246
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

403
00:19:40,246 --> 00:19:43,684
ALL YOU’RE DOING IS FORCING IT
ON YOU, AND THAT DOESN’T WORK.

404
00:19:43,684 --> 00:19:45,986
IT IS IMPRESSIVE
FOR AN ORDINARY HUMAN

405
00:19:45,986 --> 00:19:47,588
TO SURVIVE WEARING IT,
THOUGH,

406
00:19:47,588 --> 00:19:49,756
SO YOU GET AN "A"
FOR EFFORT.

407
00:19:49,756 --> 00:19:53,860
HOWEVER, IN MY OPINION,
NOTHING IS UGLIER

408
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:57,230
THAN A PERSON WEARING CLOTHES
THAT DON’T FIT THEM!

409
00:20:01,802 --> 00:20:05,071
YOUR MISTAKE WAS WEARING
JUNKETSU TO THIS BATTLE.

410
00:20:05,071 --> 00:20:06,940
A TERRIBLE MISTAKE!

411
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:10,711
ITS STRENGTH IS THE REASON
YOU HAVE THE NERVE TO FACE ME.

412
00:20:10,711 --> 00:20:13,580
YOU’D COLLAPSE
IN A HEAP WITHOUT IT!

413
00:20:15,181 --> 00:20:19,219
I’VE HEARD ENOUGH
OF YOUR GARBAGE!

414
00:20:23,056 --> 00:20:27,460
YOUR LITTLE SCHEME TODAY
HAS PROVEN QUITE ENTERTAINING.

415
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:31,364
BUT I THINK IT’S TIME
YOU RETURNED JUNKETSU NOW.

416
00:20:35,936 --> 00:20:39,706
Satsuki: [ SCREAMS ]

417
00:20:52,886 --> 00:20:53,654
[ GASPS ]

418
00:20:53,654 --> 00:20:54,955
SENKETSU: Look at the sky!

419
00:21:02,428 --> 00:21:03,664
WHAT THE HELL?

420
00:21:14,508 --> 00:21:16,476
[ ALL GASPING ]

421
00:21:16,476 --> 00:21:18,845
ARE THOSE
WHAT I THINK THEY ARE?

422
00:21:18,845 --> 00:21:19,980
Ragyo: YES.

423
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:21,882
THOSE ARE COVERS ‐‐

424
00:21:21,882 --> 00:21:25,986
BEINGS THAT WERE CREATED
FROM THE PRIMORDIAL LIFE FIBER.

425
00:21:25,986 --> 00:21:27,420
[ SHUDDERING ]

426
00:21:29,055 --> 00:21:30,591
SATSUKI!

427
00:21:33,694 --> 00:21:37,731
YOU ARE A DISGRACE,
SATSUKI KIRYUIN.

428
00:21:37,731 --> 00:21:39,700
ANYONE WHO DARES OPPOSE ME ‐‐

429
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:43,870
NO, THE LIFE FIBERS ‐‐
WILL SUFFER THE SAME FATE!

430
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:45,438
YOU BITCH!

431
00:21:45,438 --> 00:21:48,575
SATSUKI WAS NEVER A WORTHY HOST
FOR THE LIFE FIBERS.

432
00:21:48,575 --> 00:21:51,011
I, ON THE OTHER HAND, AM.

433
00:21:51,011 --> 00:21:52,378
[ WOMAN SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

434
00:21:52,378 --> 00:21:54,014
[ TWINKLE! ]

435
00:22:02,856 --> 00:22:06,192
LIFE FIBER OVERRIDE.

436
00:22:06,192 --> 00:22:08,228
KAMUI JUNKETSU.

437
00:22:08,228 --> 00:22:10,196
NO WAY.

438
00:22:10,196 --> 00:22:11,898
THANKS TO THAT FOOL
OF A DAUGHTER,

439
00:22:11,898 --> 00:22:15,168
I MET THE LAST PERSON
I EVER EXPECTED TO.

440
00:22:15,168 --> 00:22:15,969
[ GASPS ]

441
00:22:17,871 --> 00:22:19,573
[ STRAINING ]

442
00:22:23,009 --> 00:22:26,880
[ PULSING ]

443
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,749
[ HEART BEATING ]

444
00:22:33,286 --> 00:22:35,055
YOU’RE KIDDING.

445
00:22:35,055 --> 00:22:37,457
IT CAN’T BE.

446
00:22:37,457 --> 00:22:41,494
RYUKO MATOI, DON’T YOU SEE?

447
00:22:41,494 --> 00:22:45,866
YOUR BODY IS ONE
WITH THE LIFE FIBERS, LIKE MINE.

448
00:22:45,866 --> 00:22:48,502
I THOUGHT YOU WERE DEAD,
BUT NOW I KNOW.

449
00:22:48,502 --> 00:22:50,837
YOU ARE MY DAUGHTER.

450
00:22:50,837 --> 00:22:51,972
[ GASPS ]

451
00:24:23,697 --> 00:24:25,331
Senketsu: RYUKO IS UNCONSCIOUS,

452
00:24:25,331 --> 00:24:27,267
AND SATSUKI AND MAKO
ARE MISSING.

453
00:24:27,267 --> 00:24:29,603
ALL THREE ARE OUT OF ACTION
AT A TIME LIKE THIS?

454
00:24:29,603 --> 00:24:32,539
BUT THE ELITE FOUR REMAIN.
THE NAKED WARRIORS REMAIN.

455
00:24:32,539 --> 00:24:34,675
THEY’LL SHOW RAGYO
HOW HUMANS ENDURE.

456
00:24:34,675 --> 00:24:36,009
NEXT TIME ON "KILL LA KILL,"

457
00:24:36,009 --> 00:24:38,812
"RAINDROPS KEEP FALLING
